text:
dear @UPS & @UPSHelp  team
big thanks to you, my phone disappeared because of you.
it was in the repair and should have been delivered back - it never arrived. instead of hiring thieves you might consider to hire trustworthy employees. thx for nothing :)

@escapinghelll I am sorry to hear that you did not receive your package. I can only imagine just how upsetting this must be. I'd like to take a look into this on your behalf. Would you mind providing your name, tracking number, address and phone number via a DM please? Thank you. ^KD https://t.co/wKJHDXWGRQ
